# NOTE: the frontend build imports backend/common.ts and reads the root
# deno.jsonc, and vite's visualizer writes ../data/stats.html — so `backend`
# and the `data/` directory must stay in the build upload. Vercel serves only
# `dist/`, so uploaded (non-dist) files are never publicly reachable.
# We only trim the heavy/irrelevant content.
